<div class="cards">
	<div class="form-block">
		<h4>您选择了优摩卡,价值&yen;10000元</h4>
		<p>请填写用卡人信息 : </p>
		<%=form_for :member_card, :url=>confirm_user_card_path do |f|%>
			<%=f.hidden_field :id,:value=>@member_card.id%>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label">手机号码 : </label>
				<%=f.text_field :user_tel,:class=>"field-input"%>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "提交订单",:class=>"btn submit"%>
			</div>
		<%end%>
	</div>
	<div class="tips-block clearfix">
		<p>小贴士</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>为什么要填写用卡人信息?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>用卡人手机号码填错怎么办？</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="other-tip"> <span class="required">*</span> 小贴士 :  如果暂时无法确定用卡人信息请联系客服，客服电话：400-826-4568 。</div>
</div>